hem tho the crafting system is pointless aswell in the current state of the game since you need to farm a good amount for the items when you can just get a better item in the next area.i think i got everything that i wanted, i got nothing against the game its really fun if you got friends to play with and the fact that you become a cute ghost when you die is an awsome addon. i recommend that you try the game if you have at least 1 friend to play with, i look forward to uppdates and buffs to the underpowered classes.This game at it current state get a 7/10"
